                     <interp inst="t17781021-21-off115" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a cloth coat, value 12 s. and a man's hat, value 4 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17781021-21-victim195" type="victimName">
                     William
                      Edwards
                  <interp inst="t17781021-21-victim195" type="surname" value="Edwards"></interp>
